uz.mohirlab.senbrua (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Modern sound recorder for GNOME
  * Noise reduction support with audiornnoise/rnnoise
  * Multiple audio format support (OGG, MP3, M4A, FLAC, WAV, OPUS)
  * Real-time waveform visualization
  * Recording management with rename and delete functionality
  * Theme mode switching (System, Light, Dark)
  * Keyboard shortcuts dialog
  * Multi-language support including Uzbek (Latin and Cyrillic)
  * Based on Vocalis by Christopher Davis

 -- Otabek Sadiridinov <sadiridinovotabek@gmail.com>  Sat, 04 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000
